commit dbf1db2253cac6cf06488e2739068be135983682
Author: m <415fox@gmail.com>
Date:   Sat Jan 28 13:30:52 2012 -0800

    Backport ./configure --with-poller from libzmq development.
    
    If you've been configuring the poller using:
    CPPFLAGS=-DZMQ_FORCE_POLL ./configure
    
    Now you're going to want to say:
    ./configure --with-poller=poll

