commit 354faeb8360c434600b6c5e34dc1c249991bc014
Merge: 04b2ef2 1f1b454
Author: Pieter Hintjens <ph@imatix.com>
Date:   Mon Dec 5 08:18:28 2011 -0800

    Merge pull request #35 from mika-fischer/libzmq-290
    
    Use monotonic clock for clock_t

commit 1f1b4543750d9ec882cc83c3e0f49b568c57bbf5
Author: Mika Fischer <mika.fischer@zoopnet.de>
Date:   Fri Dec 2 09:43:44 2011 +0100

    Use monotonic clock for clock_t
    
    This makes clock_t insensitive to the system clock being reset by NTP or
    the sysadmin, which could previously cause long hangs for instance in
    zmq_poll.

 configure.in  |    4 ++--
