commit 561a9d2d8022d76166e1de981543337a783f6076
Merge: 69bc977 c4dabba
Author: Pieter Hintjens <ph@imatix.com>
Date:   Thu Nov 17 09:16:43 2011 -0800

    Merge pull request #32 from mika-fischer/libzmq-281
    
    Work around for LIBZMQ-281

commit c4dabba55f71d2648d9196cd5ef3b2c7238ab254
Author: Mika Fischer <mika.fischer@zoopnet.de>
Date:   Thu Nov 17 13:33:55 2011 +0100

    Work around for LIBZMQ-281
    
    The problem is that other threads might still be in mailbox::send() when
    it is destroyed. So as a workaround, we just acquire the mutex in the
    destructor. Therefore the running send will finish before the mailbox is
    destroyed.
    
    Signed-off-by: Mika Fischer <mika.fischer@zoopnet.de>

 src/mailbox.cpp |    5 +++++
 1 files changed, 5 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

